9.8.91 - 2.20.06

My best friend in the entire world. The only thing I could ever depend on. He means everything to me, and I'll miss him so much. No one can ever take his place. The best dog in the entire world, the only thing I ever loved and cared about, the only thing that kept me sane in this fucked up place. This is one thing I did not need right now.

I'll never forget you, and nothing will ever take your place.
My handsome man.

I will fuck up every fucking old peice of shit driving a car, they dont know what they're doing. 
They shouldn't be driving in the first place.

So, I've officially been through hell and back. About a week ago I was kicked out of my house, and had no where to go, and didn't wan't to be down here. So the plans were made, I was shipped off to Massachusetts to be with my family, but I end up staying with my friends most of the time. Everything was so sudden, I was going to have to leave school, and everything down here, I became so distant with everyone and it didn't matter. Also come to find out, my best friend might be moving. All of these things are falling into place. I was suppose to stay in MA for 2-3 weeks, but I end up staying 1 week maybe more. I had the time of my life up there, and it came to be that me leaving made me realize what is going for me up north, thing's started working out, and I didn't mind staying in MA, I liked the idea of it all, then I have to leave again. Hands down, Massachusetts is the most beautiful place on earth.

Props to the two best females on earth who happen to be my best friends.
Idiots Colleen&TL
